--------------------------------
--- BOMBERMINE Bukkit plugin ---
--------------------------------

VERSION 0.2
	Game:
	* Each team owns colored block of wool (a.k.a flag)
	* Configure home and team spawns
	* Players can interract with flags (pick up & drop on death)
	
VERSION 0.1
	Game:
	* Join a team manualy or with autobalance
	* Cooldown respawn
	
	Features:
	* Explosives Traps with chaining
	* Sprint accelerator blocs